            { "year": "1933", "color": "#00782A", "event": "Published", "description": "Pocket edition — 700,000 copies. A reprint is ordered within a month." },
            { "year": "1933", "color": "#1C3F95", "event": "Standard", "description": "Large-format poster editions appear. The diagram becomes the Underground's face." }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "speakerNotes": "Here's the whole arc in five steps. 1931 — Beck, laid off from the signalling office, draws the first diagram at home..."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "label": "08 A Colour Per Line",
      "screenshot": "slides/slide-08.png",
      "background": "#FFFFFF",
      "layout": "table",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text", "id": "title",
